Selected Container:-
        Editor enabled
        hover overlay removed
        Hover on individual elements enabled
        
        p,span: 
            On Hover:
                    Enable Edit tooltip 
                    Remove
                    Add an element above,below(img,p,link)
                    Move Up and down
                    Change color


            On Click:
                    Focus element on editor component
                    Click tootlip
                    Enable on editor 

            On Editor:
                    Enable: Click on page
                            Click on editor
                    Features:
                            Focus element
                            Size,Bold,Italic,Color,Text align,Background
                            Selection of text as link


        img   :
            On Hover:
                    Enable Edit tooltip 
                    Remove
                    Add an element above,below(img,p,link)
                    Move Up and down
                    Replace(Invoke or change source)
            
            On Click:
                    Focus element on editor component
                    Click tootlip
                    Enable on editor 

            On Editor:
                    Enable: Click on page
                            Click on editor
                    Features:
                            Focus element
                            Replace:Prompt user pc,change link
        
        link:
            On Hover:
                    Enable Edit tooltip 
                    Remove
                    Add an element above,below(img,p,link)
                    Move Up and down
                    Replace(Change source)
                    Replace as a section in the page
            
            On Click:
                    Focus element on editor component
                    Click tootlip
                    Enable on editor
                    Replace as a section in page:
                        Enable hover over components and select id
                
            On Editor: 
                    Enable: Click on page
                            Click on editor
                    Features:
                            Focus element
                            Replace:Prompt user pc,change link,
                            add as link to a section of the page
                    
        div:
            On Editor:
                     (parent):
                     Background colour or Image, Remove, Move, Add above or below
                     List of containers contained in it

                     (non-parent):
                     Background colour or Image,
                     List the text, images and link components contained in the container



        
            

            
                    



Add element:
                    Above: Add a (selected)section above current in the editor
                    Below: Add a (selected)section above current in the editor





Remarks/takeaways(Future development):

                        Always have all the text contents under span tag in all the future templates.
                        Always use inline style elements for all the template elements.



